---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Orlando Martinez (Lanz) — AI Specialist at DSWD Philippines, full-stack systems engineer, and AI-augmented development practitioner.">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-6 mb-8">
        <img
          src="/images/profile.jpg"
          alt="Orlando Martinez (Lanz)"
          width="128"
          height="128"
          class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover"
          style="border: 2px solid var(--color-border);"
        />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text);">About Me</h1>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">Orlando Martinez (Lanz) — AI Specialist & Full-Stack Systems Engineer</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
        <p>
          I'm Orlando Martinez (Lanz), an AI Specialist and full-stack systems engineer based in
          San Jose Del Monte City, Bulacan, Philippines. I work at the Department of Social Welfare
          and Development (DSWD), where I design and deploy intelligent document processing systems
          for government operations.
        </p>
        <p>
          My main project, the IDP System, is a production enterprise platform with multi-provider
          AI extraction, RAG-based document Q&A, human-in-the-loop review workflows, and multi-tenant
          RBAC. I built it as a solo developer using AI-augmented development — architecting the system
          myself and orchestrating AI-assisted implementation to achieve the velocity of a small team.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before DSWD, I was a Computer Programmer at the Department of Information and Communications
          Technology (DICT), where I deployed disaster risk reduction systems, built automation tools,
          and prototyped AI chatbots. I also spent time as a researcher at UP Los Ba&ntilde;os, where I built
          the wireless sensor network system that became Lo-CADIS Sprout.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Technical Skills -->
      <div class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text);">Technical Skills</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">LLM Integration (Ollama, OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, Groq), RAG/pgvector, Prompt Engineering & A/B Testing, OCR (Tesseract, EasyOCR), Document AI, Active Learning, HITL Workflows</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Backend</h3>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">Python 3.11+, FastAPI, asyncpg, Pydantic v2, Redis, WebSocket, Celery</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Frontend</h3>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">React 19, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Axios, Astro</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Database</h3>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">PostgreSQL 16, pgvector, asyncpg (raw SQL), Redis 7, TimescaleDB</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Infrastructure</h3>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">Docker Compose, MinIO/S3, Kubernetes (Helm), Ansible, Linux, Azure, GCP</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Automation & Security</h3>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">n8n Workflows, GitHub Actions, JWT Auth, RBAC, Rate Limiting, Fernet Encryption, Audit Logging</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="mt-10 p-6 rounded-xl" style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">Get in Touch</h2>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:lnzmrtnz@outlook.com">lnzmrtnz@outlook.com</a> | <a href="mailto:lanz.martinez1205@gmail.com">lanz.martinez1205@gmail.com</a></p>
          <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/KaijuBytes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/KaijuBytes</a></p>
          <p>Location: San Jose Del Monte City, Bulacan, Philippines</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
